[Student "S"]
{After NORTH opens 2NT, SOUTH is pretty sure there will be a slam in \Hs. 
But, the contract should be played from the NORTH side so the opening lead doesn't go through any vulnerable 
\S holding NORTH might have.

SOUTH transfers NORTH to \Hs, then uses Blackwood to be sure they aren't 
off two Aces. Missing one Ace he settles for 6\H.}

