[Student "S"]
{WEST has an invitational hand, (9 points), after EAST's 1NT opening. 
With a 4-card \S suit she uses Stayman.

EAST then shows his 4-card \H suit.

With no \H fit, WEST can only invite with 2NT, an invitation which 
EAST declines.}

